{
  "stem": "21582.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, and they were-- and their children were our friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, he was such a handsome, stately, tall man with this-- looks so reverent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And with this beard-- a young man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[CRYING] They ripped his beard out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They beat him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They kick him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[CRYING] I mean, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] again, what-- that it would stop-- it would, would seem to-- you know, memory is selective.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I'm glad that I had the good fortune of having these memories available to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't [LAUGHS] mean the bad ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But I mean the kindness, the warmth, and, and, and the security of my community-- and the joy and the singing and the love for nature.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I'm glad that this was available to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I hope that this is available to my progeny, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I like to share.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I always like to share the good-- the good part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there, there, there, there, there were-- there was one neighbor in our building-- it was a four-story building.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had balconies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he just went crazy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- almost every morning-- I don't know if it was every morning-- and I don't-- he, he would just pierce the silence.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, we always tried to be very inconspicuous, very unseen, very unheard, not, not to be heard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't want to provoke.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just went crazy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think that he lost his son.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was just gobbled up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He just screamed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He just wailed and just screamed every morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was-- it, it was-- it was a serious concern because there was a danger of, of, of attracting attention.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was also such a feeling of protecting him because we knew he's suffering.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
